      "date": "2015-01-20 22:48:58.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> we probably can add another test to set different time on client and MDT then check if the server use the time from client side during create striped directory and other related thing.\n\nThis is easy to do for controlled local runs but changing the clocks on autotest VMs seems like a recipe for chaos. I'll keep it in mind though.",
